The paper deals with the problem of adversarial reinforcement learning for multi-agent domains, specifically in the context of autonomous driving. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Robotics (cs.RO), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
